==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Substituent
<hw>Sub*stit"u*ent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>substituens</ets>, p. pr. See <er>Substitute</er>.]</ety>
<fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>Any atom, group, or radical substituted for
another, or entering a molecule in place of some other part which is
removed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Substitute</ent>⟦br⟧
